{"tid":1076862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本第一迷宮車站 大阪梅田","createTime":"2019-03-25T07:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T11:09:14.000Z","uid":32511,"like":44,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"8cbfdeb20584bf166021e4ec40597fb96e1174ef","tid":1076862,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://j-town.net/tokyo/research/results/277320.html?p=all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj-town.net%2Ftokyo%2Fresearch%2Fresults%2F277320.html%3Fp%3Dall&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6X%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=940e186e\" target=\"_blank\">https://j-town.net/tokyo/research/results/277320.html?p=all</a><br />\n<br />\n日本j town網路公司於2019年1月29~3月18對日本各都道府縣民眾進行民調,票選日本最強的迷宮及危險車站排行榜<br />\n<br />\n在票選中有七個車站進入排行榜,分別為東京・新宿・渋谷・池袋・横浜・大阪・名古屋等7站.<br />\n<br />\n而榮獲第一的是大阪梅田車站,而新宿駅、渋谷駅、東京駅則分居2~4名, 大阪梅田普遍得到各地區民眾的認同為第一複雜車站,該車站由於鄰接商店街及百貨加深其複雜度."},{"pid":"1b8a4069e718c259423e5109341bb148271a5474","tid":1076862,"uid":90,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新宿上次係喺百貨公司個出口蕩失路<br />\n行咗十分鐘先出到街"},{"pid":"577d772a6cbf268decb260affb95d5fd79b6777a","tid":1076862,"uid":25952,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:39:47.000Z","msg":"真心覺得佢地站內指示牌太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cab19c5d784e2b601fb39dc94787c3b84655b21","tid":1076862,"uid":196625,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:42:26.000Z","msg":"新宿東京去多幾次都慣啦, 梅田個站構咁多間公司仲大過新宿"},{"pid":"2484fddf483946f68fd6b702a0cb276559ea45e5","tid":1076862,"uid":42700,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:43:50.000Z","msg":"梅田反而好過新宿"},{"pid":"754fbd1d006121a2050adcfd710e8d224564b3e3","tid":1076862,"uid":60545,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:01:12.000Z","msg":"池袋算易喎"},{"pid"